#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cedocs-integration.md:59
msgid "Workspace naming convention"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cedocs-integration.md:61
msgid ""
"Workspaces are named `<projectNumber> — <projectName>`, e.g. `123456789 — "
"N308 Reconstructie`. The project number is used as the search key so that re-"
"deploying or restarting the process does not create duplicate workspaces."
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cedocs-integration.md:63
msgid "Document IDs"
msgstr ""

#: C:/Users/gorts01/Development/iou-architectuur/docs/en/linked-data-explorer%5Cdeveloper%5Cedocs-integration.md:65
msgid ""
"eDOCS workspace and document IDs are plain integers (e.g. `2993896`). The "
"`_restapi.ref.id` field in upload requests is passed as an integer — "
"`parseInt(workspaceId, 10)`."
msgstr ""

